National Distillers andChemical Corp said it completed the sale of Almaden VineyardsInc to Heublein Inc for about 128 mln dlrs.    Heublein, a former subsidiary of RJR Nabisco Inc &lt;RJR>, wasrecently acquired by &lt;Grand Metropolitan PLC>.    Almaden, based in San Jose, Calif., makes and sells tablewines, champagnes and brandies as well as some premium winesunder the Charles Lefranc Cellars label.  Reuter&#3;